<chapter id="foundation_messagesource">
	<title>Configuration</title>
	<para>
		The following is a part of context-message.xml file which defines messageSource
		newly added by Foundation Plugin installation.
	</para>
	<programlisting language="xml"><![CDATA[<bean id="messageSource" class="]]><emphasis role="bold"><![CDATA[anyframe.common.context.support.EncodingResourceBundleMessageSource]]></emphasis><![CDATA[">
    <property name="basenames">
        <list>
            <value>message/message-moviefinder</value>
            <value>message/message-converter</value>
            <value>anyframe/core/ria/mip/messages/mip</value>
            <value>anyframe/core/hibernate/messages/hibernate</value>
            <value>anyframe/core/idgen/messages/idgeneration</value>
            <value>anyframe/core/properties/messages/properties</value>
            <value>anyframe/core/query/messages/query</value>
            <value>anyframe/core/query/ria/messages/riaquery</value>
            <value>anyframe/web/springmvc/messages/springmvc</value>
            <value>anyframe/iam/security</value>
        </list>
    </property>
    ]]><emphasis role="bold"><![CDATA[<property name="defaultEncoding">
        <value>UTF-8</value>
    </property>]]></emphasis><![CDATA[
</bean>]]></programlisting>
	<para>
		Define encoding by defining EncodingResourceBundleMessageSource as messageSource bean as above
		and using defaultEncoding property.
		If no definition is set, it well be set as "UTF-8".		
	</para>
</chapter>